Canny Defense	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DEFINE:CannyDefenseLVL|0													BONUS:COMBAT|AC|max(0,min(INT,CannyDefenseLVL))|TYPE=Ability.STACK|PREMULT:2,[!PREEQUIP:1,TYPE=Armor,TYPE=Shield],[PREEQUIP:1,TYPE=Melee]														SOURCEPAGE:PrestigeClasses.rtf												BENEFIT:When not wearing armor or using a shield, a duelist adds 1 point of Intelligence bonus (if any) per duelist class level to her Dexterity bonus to modify Armor Class while wielding a melee weapon. If a duelist is caught flat-footed or otherwise denied her Dexterity bonus, she also loses this bonus.
